			<h2>Music Ministry</h2>
			<p>These choirs provide music ministry on a regular monthly schedule for the regular Sunday services at the church. They sing at various special services, functions and programs held by or at the church. They travel with the pastor to sing for various services and events. They are invited to sing at various church and community event.  Each choir also has an anniversary performance each year.</p>

			<p>The Angelic Celestial Choir, Mass Choir and Male Chorus are directed by Brother Alvin Stansbury (Keyboard) supported by his son David Stansbury (Drums) and other musicians. The Inspirational Choir and Junior Choir are directed by Brother Donald Hunt (Keyboard), support by his son Donald Hunt Jr. (Drums) and other musicians.</p>
