			<p>Come be apart of the Women's Ministry at Asbury Broadneck Church.  We are women who are on a mission for the Lord.  Enjoy food, fellowship and fun at the same time we will be working unto the glory of the Lord.  Women's Ministry supports Bible study, discussion groups and fellowship activities specifically designed for women of all ages.   The mission of Women's Ministry is to reach women where they are on their journey with Christ.  Sister Virginia Thomas, Chairperson.</p>
